Package: nitro
Type: Package
Title: Integration of TNT in R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Tom Brougham
Maintainer: Tom Brougham <tbrougham@paravian.net>
Description: Integration of the phylogenetics software TNT (Goloboff et al.
    2008, Goloboff and Catalano 2016) in R. It interfaces with a locally
    installed copy of the TNT command-line program and provides functions for
    performing branch swapping, parsimony ratchet and driven (i.e., "New
    Technology") searches. Each tree search function automatically returns
    a set of trees for visualisation or use with other R packages.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
